threshing floor of Araunah within the citadel of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=24&verse=16'>2Sa 24:16</a><br/> David purchases and erects an altar upon it<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=24&verse=25'>2Sa 24:25</a><br/> The city built around the citadel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=11&verse=8'>1Ch 11:8</a><br/> Fortified by Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=3&verse=1'>1Ki 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=15'>1Ki 9:15</a><br/> The temple built within the citadel<br/> <a href='S:Temple'>Temple</a><br/> Captured and pillaged by:<br/> - Shishak, king of Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=26'>1Ki 14:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=12&verse=9'>2Ch 12:9</a> <br/> - Jehoash, king of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=14'>2Ki 14:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=25&verse=24'>2Ch 25:24</a> <br/> - Nebuchadnezzar, king of Babylon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=24&verse=16'>2Ki 24:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=17'>2Ki 25:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=36&verse=21'>2Ch 36:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=1&verse=3'>Jer 1:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=32&verse=2'>Jer 32:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=39'>Jer 39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=52&verse=7'>Jer 52:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=52&verse=24'>Jer 52:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=1&verse=8'>Lam 1:8</a> <br/> Walls of, restored and fortified:<br/> - By Uzziah<br/> <a href='https://www.wor